A vide-poche is a receptacle into which the contents of a gentleman’s pocket can be emptied, or studs and cufflinks can be placed when disrobing. It traditionally sits on a dressing table. This sublime example is carved from aventurine quartz and is by Carl Fabergé. https://t.co/1cFmoe9dTo
